<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ludwig III. von Wittelsbach, Pfalzgraf bei Rhein</head><p>Der Rat kündigt seinen Diener Hans Maurer wegen der Herren von Hanau an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_146" id="72v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_146_r1l16">Dem <expan>Durchleuht<ex>igen</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>geporn</ex></expan> <expan>furſt<ex>en</ex></expan> etc Hercʒog Ludweigen pfalcʒgrafen beẏ Rein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_146_r1l17"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / VVir ſenden cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>durchleuht<ex>ikeit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l18">Hanſen 
<del rend="strikethrough">M </del> <expan>Maur<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l19">cʒu reden von der von Hanaw vvegen / Als der vormals </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l20">auch darümb beẏ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gevveſe<ex>n</ex></expan> iſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l21">vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_146" id="72v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem <expan>durchleuht<ex>igen</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>hoch<ex>geporn</ex></expan>
<expan>furst<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. herczog Ludweigen, pfalczgrafen bey
                        Rein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir senden czu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>durchleuht<ex>ikeit</ex></expan> Hansen
                            <expan>Maur<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener,
                        mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> czu reden von der von Hanaw wegen, als der
                        vormals auch darümb bey <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> ist. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>
                        etc. ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
